{"word":"φαρμακεία","slug":"φαρμακεία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φαρμακεία</b></el> <el>(φαρμᾰκείᾱ, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φαρμακεύω'><el>φαρμακεύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>the use of drugs, potions, spells</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>poisoning, witchcraft</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>veneficium</el>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>remedy, cure</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}